393
00:20:15,460 --> 00:20:16,460
This isn't my decision.

394
00:20:16,580 --> 00:20:17,740
It's made by the leaders.

395
00:20:18,420 --> 00:20:19,460
This event

396
00:20:19,580 --> 00:20:21,700
