399
00:20:24,700 --> 00:20:25,940
Why can't Liu Wanqing represent

400
00:20:25,940 --> 00:20:27,180
our school's image?

401
00:20:28,300 --> 00:20:30,060
This decision was made by my superiors.

402
00:20:30,380 --> 00:20:32,540
The school leaders
held a meeting this morning.

403
00:20:33,100 --> 00:20:35,580
This event isn't just for entertainment.

404
00:20:35,780 --> 00:20:37,260
Many factors have to be considered.

405
00:20:37,260 --> 00:20:40,380
Academic performance, knowledge,
appearance, image,

406
00:20:40,380 --> 00:20:41,220
temperament,

407
00:20:41,380 --> 00:20:43,380
