424
00:21:13,580 --> 00:21:14,420
Ka Men.

425
00:21:14,820 --> 00:21:15,660
Ka Men!

426
00:21:17,460 --> 00:21:18,300
Director Wu,

427
00:21:18,500 --> 00:21:20,260
I think she and I work really well together.

428
00:21:20,500 --> 00:21:21,420
She's helped me a lot.

429
00:21:21,620 --> 00:21:23,060
- No need to replace...
- Enough!

430
00:21:23,060 --> 00:21:24,060
The decision is final.

431
00:21:26,940 --> 00:21:27,780
Lu Yao,

432
