467
00:23:21,300 --> 00:23:22,140
Liu Wanqing,

468
00:23:23,460 --> 00:23:25,100
first of all,

469
00:23:26,020 --> 00:23:27,540
I want you to know

470
00:23:28,220 --> 00:23:29,780
