523
00:25:34,100 --> 00:25:34,940
Ka Men,

524
00:25:35,140 --> 00:25:35,980
don't force it.

525
00:25:36,080 --> 00:25:37,300
Let's go back to the classroom.

526
00:25:37,300 --> 00:25:38,140
Exactly.

527
00:25:38,220 --> 00:25:39,660
I promised Mr. Zhou

528
00:25:39,900 --> 00:25:41,780
I'd be our class's tour guide
this afternoon.

529
00:25:42,340 --> 00:25:43,780
You're still going?

530
00:25:47,260 --> 00:25:48,100
Liu Wanqing!

531
00:25:50,380 --> 00:25:51,220
I have to go.

532
00:25:54,900 --> 00:25:56,020
They're just bullying her!

533
00:25:56,260 --> 00:25:57,300
- Exactly!
- Exactly!

534
00:25:57,300 --> 00:25:58,820
Go stand with them.

535
00:26:03,760 --> 00:26:04,900
Alright, Mr. Zhou.

536
00:26:04,900 --> 00:26:06,220
We can discuss things then.

537
00:26:06,220 --> 00:26:07,290
Okay, no problem.

538
00:26:12,300 --> 00:26:14,140
Ka Men's been treated so unfairly.

539
00:26:17,500 --> 00:26:18,660
We can't just let this slide!

540
00:26:20,300 --> 00:26:21,740
