00:27:39,020 --> 00:27:40,420
How do you learn a foreign language?

576
00:27:40,740 --> 00:27:42,740
I learn English by listening to

577
00:27:42,740 --> 00:27:43,900
English songs.

578
00:27:44,420 --> 00:27:46,060
If you want to learn Chinese,

579
00:27:46,060 --> 00:27:48,940
you can start by
listening to Chinese songs too.

580
00:27:49,780 --> 00:27:51,020
Such as Jasmine.

581
00:27:51,940 --> 00:27:52,780
Okay.

582
00:27:52,940 --> 00:27:54,670
Let's start the campus tour,

583
00:27:54,690 --> 00:27:55,530
shall we?

584
00:27:55,540 --> 00:27:56,380
Yeah, please.

585
00:27:57,140 --> 00:27:57,980
Come here.

586
00:27:58,660 --> 00:27:59,500
This way.

587
00:27:59,770 --> 00:28:01,260
This is our library.

588
00:28:02,260 --> 00:28:04,460
There is a big playground in our school.

589
00:28:04,460 --> 00:28:06,220
We often play basketball there.

590
00:28:06,220 --> 00:28:07,420
Where's the library?

591
00:28:07,420 --> 00:28:09,460
The library is in the south corner.

592
00:28:09,460 --> 00:28:10,300
This way.

593
00:28:13,420 --> 00:28:14,260
Go this way.

594
00:28:29,980 --> 00:28:34,460
(Warmly welcome textile workers to apply
for the flight attendant position)

595
00:28:53,420 --> 00:28:54,260
Look, look!

596
00:28:54,260 --> 00:28:55,360
I'll get the sign-up form.

597
00:28:55,780 --> 00:28:57,500
The sign-up form is here, right?

598
00:28:57,740 --> 00:28:58,580
Excuse me,

599
00:28:58,860 --> 00:29:00,380
let me grab it first!

600
00:29:00,380 --> 00:29:01,580
There sure are a lot of people.

601
00:29:05,020 --> 00:29:05,860
Pei!

602
00:29:06,180 --> 00:29:07,020
What are you doing?

603
00:29:07,100 --> 00:29:08,180
- Pei.
- Come inside!

604
00:29:13,620 --> 00:29:14,740
Go in, go in.

605
00:29:15,460 --> 00:29:17,220
- Zhang Qiming!
- You're not the gatekeeper.

606
00:29:17,700 --> 00:29:19,290
- You've made it this far.
- Come on in!

607
00:29:19,540 --> 00:29:20,380
What's wrong?

608
00:29:24,540 --> 00:29:25,380
The sign-up form.

609
00:29:28,740 --> 00:29:29,560
The sign-up form.

610
00:29:31,060 --> 00:29:32,220
Look at them.

611
00:29:33,180 --> 00:29:35,180
They're all so young.

612
00:29:38,500 --> 00:29:40,100
All the applicants are young.

613
00:29:41,060 --> 00:29:41,900
Didn't they say

614
00:29:42,260 --> 00:29:44,700
the position was for women aged 40-50?

615
00:29:45,630 --> 00:29:47,220
What are they doing here?

616
00:29:49,740 --> 00:29:51,180
Pei, don't be afraid.

617
00:29:51,540 --> 00:29:52,460
Stand straight.

618
00:29:52,780 --> 00:29:54,740
- Stand straight!
- I just can't!

619
00:29:58,980 --> 00:29:59,860
I'm quitting.

620
00:30:00,700 --> 00:30:01,540
Why?

621
00:30:02,180 --> 00:30:03,020
I...

622
00:30:03,900 --> 00:30:04,740
What?

623
00:30:05,780 --> 00:30:07,300
My qipao split.

624
00:30:07,660 --> 00:30:09,260
Where?

625
00:30:11,100 --> 00:30:11,940
Right here.

626
00:30:11,950 --> 00:30:12,800
No!

627
00:30:12,810 --> 00:30:13,850
It's perfectly fine!

628
00:30:14,460 --> 00:30:15,700
- No?
- It didn't split.

629
00:30:15,700 --> 00:30:17,380
Then it's here.

630
00:30:18,580 --> 00:30:20,020
- It didn't either!
- It's alright.

631
00:30:20,260 --> 00:30:21,800
- Really?
- Don't worry.

632
00:30:21,980 --> 00:30:23,380
The tailor I hired from Suzhou

633
00:30:23,380 --> 00:30:24,380
has amazing skills.

634
00:30:28,460 --> 00:30:29,300
Pei,

635
00:30:30,300 --> 00:30:31,820
you're just imagining it.

636
00:30:32,260 --> 00:30:33,700
Why are you so nervous?

637
00:30:34,060 --> 00:30:34,900
Don't forget

638
00:30:34,940 --> 00:30:36,820
that we've been practicing for so long.

639
00:30:37,070 --> 00:30:38,790
It's time to show off
what we've worked on.

640
00:30:40,090 --> 00:30:40,940
Exactly!

641
00:30:40,940 --> 00:30:41,860
That's right.

642
00:30:42,780 --> 00:30:43,700
But my qipao seems to

643
00:30:43,700 --> 00:30:44,900
have a life of its own.

644
00:30:44,900 --> 00:30:46,660
Who knows when it will split?

645
00:30:47,140 --> 00:30:47,980
Pei,

646
00:30:48,780 --> 00:30:50,140
Fangfang's tailor

647
00:30:50,300 --> 00:30:51,460
is top-notch!

648
00:30:51,460 --> 00:30:52,900
You can move around.
It won't...

649
00:30:52,900 --> 00:30:53,990
- split.
- How about this…

650
00:30:54,620 --> 00:30:55,660
What was that noise?

651
00:30:58,620 --> 00:30:59,700
- Did it split?
- It did!

652
00:31:00,500 --> 00:31:01,340
Come!

653
00:31:04,780 --> 00:31:05,860
Help me check!

654
00:31:06,100 --> 00:31:06,940
It did split.

655
00:31:07,460 --> 00:31:08,300
Be careful.

656
00:31:10,420 --> 00:31:11,340
So many trees.

657
00:31:11,340 --> 00:31:12,620
I'm like in a garden now.

658
00:31:12,780 --> 00:31:14,340
Yeah, our school

659
00:31:14,340 --> 00:31:15,860
was built in 1931.

660
00:31:17,100 --> 00:31:18,220
Yeah, 1931.

661
00:31:18,500 --> 00:31:20,140
We have a long history.

662
00:31:20,700 --> 00:31:21,820
Yeah, I see.

663
00:31:29,460 --> 00:31:31,260
You really poured the whole bag in?

664
00:31:31,260 --> 00:31:32,100
Yeah,

665
00:31:32,380 --> 00:31:33,300
I poured it all in!

666
00:31:34,140 --> 00:31:35,580
Thanks for your help, Lu Yao!

667
00:31:35,780 --> 00:31:37,580
If you hadn't warned us in time,

668
00:31:37,780 --> 00:31:39,250
Qian Jiayue and I wouldn't have known

669
00:31:39,530 --> 00:31:40,500
Miejue was back.

670
00:31:40,780 --> 00:31:41,980
Qian Jiayue is the real hero.

671
00:31:42,060 --> 00:31:42,900
Did you see how she

672
00:31:42,910 --> 00:31:43,920
rushed out to stop Miejue?

673
00:31:44,140 --> 00:31:44,980
True.

674
00:31:45,020 --> 00:31:46,170
Glad she thought of that.

675
00:31:46,380 --> 00:31:47,860
An interview for the school journal?

676
00:31:47,860 --> 00:31:49,540
We've given Ka Men some justice.

677
00:31:50,020 --> 00:31:50,860
Yeah.

678
00:31:50,860 --> 00:31:51,700
Yes!

679
00:31:54,860 --> 00:31:56,580
Chemistry lab. Do you have one?

680
00:31:57,180 --> 00:31:58,220
Of course!

681
00:31:58,620 --> 00:32:00,020
- Let me show you.
- Okay.

682
00:32:00,620 --> 00:32:01,460
This way.

683
00:32:04,780 --> 00:32:05,620
Look!

684
00:32:05,630 --> 00:32:07,100
How's it going? Is it sewn up?

685
00:32:07,100 --> 00:32:08,620
No problem at all!

686
00:32:08,620 --> 00:32:10,140
Really, no traces left at all.

687
00:32:10,140 --> 00:32:11,600
I'm lucky you brought the sewing kit.

688
00:32:12,980 --> 00:32:15,020
My thread snapped a few times.

689
00:32:15,020 --> 00:32:15,940
I brought it

690
00:32:15,940 --> 00:32:16,980
just in case.

691
00:32:18,020 --> 00:32:19,740
And guess what? Your thread didn't snap,

692
00:32:19,740 --> 00:32:20,740
but mine did.

693
00:32:21,740 --> 00:32:23,060
My clothes didn't snap,

694
00:32:23,060 --> 00:32:24,580
but my mind snapped.

695
00:32:25,980 --> 00:32:27,500
Okay, you go.

696
00:32:27,500 --> 00:32:28,420
I'm not going.

697
00:32:28,780 --> 00:32:29,940
It's too embarrassing.

698
00:32:31,740 --> 00:32:33,420
(Important Notes for Applicants)
Pei.

699
00:32:33,420 --> 00:32:34,860
We've come this far.

700
00:32:35,020 --> 00:32:36,100
Are you sure about this?

701
00:32:39,340 --> 00:32:40,860
I don't want to deceive myself.

702
00:32:41,780 --> 00:32:42,420
I knew

703
00:32:42,420 --> 00:32:43,700
I'd make a fool of myself,

704
00:32:44,580 --> 00:32:46,580
but I was pretending it was just for fun.

705
00:32:51,180 --> 00:32:52,620
But you guys are different.

706
00:32:53,060 --> 00:32:54,260
You're all

707
00:32:54,420 --> 00:32:55,660
so much prettier

708
00:32:55,860 --> 00:32:57,460
than those young girls.

709
00:33:00,140 --> 00:33:01,140
Don't worry about me!

710
00:33:01,140 --> 00:33:02,620
I'll go home soon.

711
00:33:03,580 --> 00:33:04,420
Some things need to

712
00:33:04,420 --> 00:33:05,340
be sorted out.

713
00:33:06,020 --> 00:33:06,860
Right?

714
00:33:07,780 --> 00:33:08,620
Alright!

715
00:33:08,700 --> 00:33:09,580
Hurry. You go on in.

716
00:33:09,980 --> 00:33:10,820
Just go.

717
00:33:11,140 --> 00:33:11,980
Give me back my bag.

718
00:33:11,990 --> 00:33:13,060
You've already entered,

719
00:33:13,060 --> 00:33:14,540
- and you've signed up.
- Zhang Qi...

720
00:33:14,540 --> 00:33:15,160
Even if

721
00:33:15,160 --> 00:33:16,670
- you won't make it,
- Come back here!

722
00:33:16,740 --> 00:33:17,870
you can still work as a chef!

723
00:33:19,060 --> 00:33:19,900
I made it!

724
00:33:20,740 --> 00:33:21,780
Missed the No. 17 bus,

725
00:33:22,340 --> 00:33:23,740
so I took a taxi.

726
00:33:24,380 --> 00:33:25,940
I thought you started the interview.

727
00:33:26,660 --> 00:33:27,580
The qipao split.

728
00:33:29,660 --> 00:33:30,740
I sewed it so many times!

729
00:33:30,740 --> 00:33:31,620
Isn't it fine?

730
00:33:32,980 --> 00:33:34,260
You sewed it?

731
00:33:54,220 --> 00:33:55,380
It's not Pei's qipao,

732
00:33:55,380 --> 00:33:57,220
it's mine that split.

733
00:33:58,040 --> 00:33:58,900
I didn't notice,

734
00:33:58,900 --> 00:34:01,100
Liu Dagui, you know how to sew?

735
00:34:01,660 --> 00:34:02,740
I can do everything

736
00:34:02,740 --> 00:34:03,700
except fixing airplanes.

737
00:34:03,900 --> 00:34:04,740
Stop bragging.

738
00:34:04,780 --> 00:34:05,620
Alright.

739
00:34:07,140 --> 00:34:07,980
Here.

740
00:34:08,220 --> 00:34:09,060
What?

741
00:34:09,940 --> 00:34:11,820
I thought it over. I already bought this.

742
00:34:12,040 --> 00:34:13,660
I'll regret it if I don't bring it to you.

743
00:34:13,700 --> 00:34:14,740
Pin it on the qipao

744
00:34:15,060 --> 00:34:16,180
to complete the look.

745
00:34:19,340 --> 00:34:21,060
Why did you buy this?

746
00:34:21,940 --> 00:34:22,970
I don't have secret money.

747
00:34:23,660 --> 00:34:25,540
I taught someone to dance
and made extra money.

748
00:34:26,820 --> 00:34:28,020
Who did you teach?

749
00:34:30,540 --> 00:34:31,620
Li Qin's husband.

750
00:34:34,380 --> 00:34:36,180
You taught the pilot to dance?

751
00:34:37,980 --> 00:34:40,140
I went to the community
activity center to dance.

752
00:34:40,460 --> 00:34:42,500
Li Qin and her husband were there.

753
00:34:42,820 --> 00:34:43,940
They said they needed to

754
00:34:43,940 --> 00:34:45,060
learn ballroom

755
00:34:45,060 --> 00:34:46,020
for a business event

756
00:34:46,020 --> 00:34:46,940
and asked me for help.

757
00:34:47,580 --> 00:34:49,140
Push your hands.

758
00:34:49,420 --> 00:34:51,340
Curl them!

759
00:34:51,780 --> 00:34:52,620
Look.

760
00:34:54,140 --> 00:34:54,980
Good!

761
00:34:55,860 --> 00:34:57,340
- No problem.
- I think so.

762
00:34:57,340 --> 00:34:58,970
- No problem at all.
- Pei, you are here.

763
00:34:59,140 --> 00:35:00,460
Honey, come learn.

764
00:35:00,460 --> 00:35:01,300
Your turn.

765
00:35:03,180 --> 00:35:04,100
You two dance so well,

766
00:35:04,380 --> 00:35:06,060
but I can't do it.

767
00:35:06,060 --> 00:35:07,380
No worries, we'll take it slow.

768
00:35:11,020 --> 00:35:13,180
So... you went to their home to...

769
00:35:13,740 --> 00:35:14,900
How do you know that?

770
00:35:16,220 --> 00:35:18,540
Yes, you both live in Jinxiu Garden!

771
00:35:19,180 --> 00:35:20,420
Li Qin's husband

772
00:35:20,540 --> 00:35:21,900
is so busy that he couldn't make it

773
00:35:21,900 --> 00:35:23,380
to the activity center,

774
00:35:23,940 --> 00:35:25,540
so I went to teach him at their home.

775
00:35:25,820 --> 00:35:27,580
I charged an extra 50 yuan
for home visits.

776
00:35:27,980 --> 00:35:28,920
Three days for 500 yuan.

777
00:35:29,140 --> 00:35:30,500
A brooch for 498.

778
00:35:31,300 --> 00:35:32,500
498?

779
00:35:36,980 --> 00:35:37,980
Oh no,

780
00:35:38,300 --> 00:35:40,060
looks like we wronged Liu Dagui.

781
00:35:40,580 --> 00:35:41,660
I told you

782
00:35:41,660 --> 00:35:43,180
not to judge too early.

783
00:35:43,580 --> 00:35:45,460
It's all my fault. I shouldn't have...

784
00:35:45,580 --> 00:35:46,420
What's going on?

785
00:35:46,980 --> 00:35:47,820
What?

786
00:35:51,100 --> 00:35:53,460
Well, we'll let you guys chat.

787
00:35:53,620 --> 00:35:54,740
Let's go upstairs.

788
00:35:54,740 --> 00:35:56,140
Come on, I'll go with you two.

789
00:35:56,380 --> 00:35:58,620
- Let's go.
- There's nothing to talk about!

790
00:35:59,560 --> 00:36:00,450
Xiu'e!

791
00:36:00,460 --> 00:36:01,980
What's with them? Out of their minds?

792
00:36:03,620 --> 00:36:04,460
I get it now.

793
00:36:05,540 --> 00:36:07,380
Did you see me with Li Qin?

794
00:36:08,220 --> 00:36:09,180
That's why

795
00:36:09,180 --> 00:36:11,100
you've been cold to me
these past few days.

796
00:36:12,840 --> 00:36:14,540
Isn't it your fault
for not saying earlier?

797
00:36:16,380 --> 00:36:17,260
Feeling guilty?

798
00:36:18,180 --> 00:36:19,660
What guilt?

799
00:36:20,860 --> 00:36:22,820
What do I have to feel guilty about?

800
00:36:23,140 --> 00:36:24,300
Quiet!

801
00:36:25,060 --> 00:36:27,060
I know you don't like Li Qin,

802
00:36:27,380 --> 00:36:29,260
and I want you to focus on the interview.

803
00:36:29,260 --> 00:36:30,100
Fine, fine!

804
00:36:30,300 --> 00:36:31,860
I just wanted to make some extra money

805
00:36:31,860 --> 00:36:33,140
to buy this for you.

806
00:36:35,380 --> 00:36:36,220
Li Qin is

807
00:36:36,340 --> 00:36:37,580
so sweet and gentle.

808
00:36:37,980 --> 00:36:39,980
Even if she didn't pay you,
you'd still be happy.

809
00:36:40,150 --> 00:36:41,020
Come on!

810
00:36:41,020 --> 00:36:41,770
Don't you know

811
00:36:41,770 --> 00:36:42,820
what kind of person she is?

812
00:36:43,540 --> 00:36:44,420
What kind of person?

813
00:36:44,420 --> 00:36:45,260
A drama queen!

814
00:36:45,740 --> 00:36:47,500
I figured her out a long time ago.

815
00:36:47,780 --> 00:36:49,220
You know, her current husband

816
00:36:49,220 --> 00:36:50,860
is so worn out because of her.

817
00:36:51,900 --> 00:36:54,580
Also, her sense of rhythm is terrible.

818
00:36:54,940 --> 00:36:55,780
Her coordination

819
00:36:55,780 --> 00:36:57,460
and flexibility are worse than yours.

820
00:36:58,260 --> 00:37:00,020
After this interview,

821
00:37:00,040 --> 00:37:01,140
I'll teach you how to dance.

822
00:37:01,540 --> 00:37:02,700
We'll dance together,

823
00:37:02,800 --> 00:37:04,940
and I won't have to look for
a dance partner anymore!

824
00:37:06,020 --> 00:37:07,820
Who said I'm dancing with you?

825
00:37:08,140 --> 00:37:09,460
Alright, alright, come here.

826
00:37:09,740 --> 00:37:10,580
Put it on.

827
00:37:11,580 --> 00:37:12,980
I don't want your roast duck.

828
00:37:13,940 --> 00:37:15,300
Swan! A white swan!

829
00:37:15,300 --> 00:37:16,540
Worth 498 yuan!

830
00:37:16,540 --> 00:37:17,380
Fine! I'll wear it!

831
00:37:18,940 --> 00:37:19,780
Pei!

832
00:37:20,620 --> 00:37:21,460
Are you ready?

833
00:37:25,820 --> 00:37:27,380
If you two have private matters,

834
00:37:27,540 --> 00:37:28,580
go home and talk!

835
00:37:28,860 --> 00:37:29,820
Old couple,

836
00:37:29,820 --> 00:37:30,660
no private matters!

837
00:37:30,820 --> 00:37:31,700
I'm coming.

838
00:37:40,540 --> 00:37:41,380
Do it.

839
00:37:42,820 --> 00:37:43,660
Do what?

840
00:37:45,580 --> 00:37:46,540
Do it.

841
00:37:49,660 --> 00:37:51,180
So many people here. So embarrassing.

842
00:37:51,780 --> 00:37:52,620
Do it!

843
00:37:58,860 --> 00:38:00,380
Who asked you to dance?

844
00:38:00,540 --> 00:38:02,420
I asked you to wipe my forehead!

845
00:38:02,420 --> 00:38:03,500
Your forehead isn't sweaty!

846
00:38:07,180 --> 00:38:08,020
Get lost.

847
00:38:09,100 --> 00:38:10,220
Don't forget to wear it!

848
00:38:10,220 --> 00:38:11,060
I heard you!

849
00:38:14,620 --> 00:38:18,060
Now, here comes our show!

850
00:38:18,820 --> 00:38:19,660
Music!

851
00:38:21,550 --> 00:38:23,250
Go. You go first.

852
00:38:23,540 --> 00:38:24,940
Slow down. Slow down.

853
00:38:29,820 --> 00:38:33,280
♪My longing♪

854
00:38:33,730 --> 00:38:37,090
♪Is an invisible net♪

855
00:38:38,370 --> 00:38:42,060
♪My longing♪

856
00:38:42,680 --> 00:38:46,530
♪Is no longer the sea breaking its banks♪

857
00:38:46,910 --> 00:38:50,370
♪Why do I always♪

858
00:38:50,650 --> 00:38:54,830
♪Think of you so deeply♪

859
00:38:55,390 --> 00:39:01,890
♪On those rainy days♪

860
00:39:04,100 --> 00:39:09,140
(Welcome—you—future air stewardesses!)

861
00:39:27,140 --> 00:39:28,380
Sisters, your performance just now

862
00:39:28,380 --> 00:39:29,740
was absolutely stunning!

863
00:39:30,260 --> 00:39:31,180
Congratulations!

864
00:39:33,620 --> 00:39:34,460
Amazing!

865
00:39:34,500 --> 00:39:35,860
You're truly our role models!

866
00:39:37,020 --> 00:39:38,420
It was so beautiful!

867
00:39:40,260 --> 00:39:41,300
Alright.

868
00:39:41,740 --> 00:39:43,700
We're flattered. You're really kind to say so.

869
00:39:44,020 --> 00:39:44,860
Yeah.

870
00:39:44,940 --> 00:39:46,540
We've already exchanged numbers.

871
00:39:46,540 --> 00:39:48,420
We'll keep in touch.

872
00:39:48,820 --> 00:39:50,140
- Sure.
- Let's stay in touch!

873
00:39:51,060 --> 00:39:52,740
We hope to hear good news from you!

874
00:39:54,740 --> 00:39:56,540
Goodbye.

875
00:39:56,540 --> 00:39:58,580
Grab a few more coupons.

876
00:39:59,130 --> 00:40:00,020
You'll have good news for sure!

877
00:40:00,020 --> 00:40:01,620
Be sure to come eat at my restaurant!

878
00:40:01,900 --> 00:40:03,540
What's the result?

879
00:40:03,660 --> 00:40:05,300
- What's the result?
- Did you make it?

880
00:40:06,620 --> 00:40:07,460
We didn't pass.

881
00:40:07,860 --> 00:40:09,100
We got eliminated.

882
00:40:10,700 --> 00:40:11,540
You're lying!

883
00:40:11,540 --> 00:40:12,700
Then how come you're so happy?

884
00:40:12,700 --> 00:40:14,360
- That's right!
- They don't believe us.

885
00:40:14,460 --> 00:40:15,940
We really didn't make it.

886
00:40:16,300 --> 00:40:17,140
It's true.

887
00:40:17,150 --> 00:40:18,030
But…

888
00:40:18,140 --> 00:40:19,700
we were only one vote short.

889
00:40:20,500 --> 00:40:21,460
That's such a pity!

890
00:40:22,300 --> 00:40:23,860
Secretary Yu encouraged us.

891
00:40:23,860 --> 00:40:24,900
He said we were graceful

892
00:40:25,100 --> 00:40:26,900
and confident during the performance.

893
00:40:27,380 --> 00:40:29,340
There will be many more opportunities.

894
00:40:29,860 --> 00:40:30,900
He even invited us

895
00:40:31,220 --> 00:40:32,380
to perform

896
00:40:32,380 --> 00:40:33,700
at their annual gathering!

897
00:40:34,260 --> 00:40:35,100
Really?

898
00:40:35,300 --> 00:40:36,620
That means your performance

899
00:40:36,620 --> 00:40:37,900
must have been spectacular!

900
00:40:37,900 --> 00:40:39,260
Incredible!

901
00:40:39,260 --> 00:40:41,140
This is what we call "defeat with honor"!

902
00:40:41,460 --> 00:40:42,340
Yes, yes!

903
00:40:42,340 --> 00:40:43,580
Old but vigorous!

904
00:40:46,730 --> 00:40:47,570
Who's old?

905
00:40:48,040 --> 00:40:48,980
That's not what I mean.

906
00:40:49,140 --> 00:40:50,660
What's next? Go home?

907
00:40:50,780 --> 00:40:52,340
Alright, we're going home.

908
00:40:53,300 --> 00:40:54,140
Excuse me!

909
00:40:54,440 --> 00:40:55,870
I'm a reporter from the Evening News.

910
00:40:55,900 --> 00:40:57,820
Your performance during the interview

911
00:40:58,140 --> 00:40:59,100
really moved me.

912
00:40:59,100 --> 00:41:01,340
Would it be okay if I interviewed you?

913
00:41:03,140 --> 00:41:04,340
Xinmin Evening News?

914
00:41:04,940 --> 00:41:06,260
What else would it be in Shanghai?

915
00:41:06,540 --> 00:41:07,380
Yes.

916
00:41:07,660 --> 00:41:09,900
Interview… us?

917
00:41:10,460 --> 00:41:11,300
Is that alright?

918
00:41:11,540 --> 00:41:12,380
Of course.

919
00:41:12,460 --> 00:41:13,580
What would you like to ask?

920
00:41:14,300 --> 00:41:15,340
Great! But first,

921
00:41:15,460 --> 00:41:16,460
let the photographer

922
00:41:16,460 --> 00:41:17,860
take a picture of you, okay?

923
00:41:18,020 --> 00:41:19,020
Sure, sure!

924
00:41:19,940 --> 00:41:21,700
Not including the two gentlemen.

925
00:41:21,700 --> 00:41:22,590
- Thank you.
- Okay.

926
00:41:22,820 --> 00:41:23,780
Stand away.

927
00:41:23,780 --> 00:41:25,220
- Join us.
- I'll pass on this one.

928
00:41:25,220 --> 00:41:26,060
Go on, go on!

929
00:41:26,340 --> 00:41:27,860
- Come on, Fangfang!
- Come on!

930
00:41:28,060 --> 00:41:29,380
Let's have four of you together!

931
00:41:29,620 --> 00:41:31,100
- Perfect.
- Come, stand here.

932
00:41:31,100 --> 00:41:31,940
Let's get ready.

933
00:41:32,340 --> 00:41:33,200
- Look here.
- Ready?

934
00:41:33,530 --> 00:41:34,370
Okay.

935
00:41:35,100 --> 00:41:36,860
Three, two, one!

936
00:41:38,100 --> 00:41:39,860
Could you relax a little more?

937
00:41:40,000 --> 00:41:40,900
Bring the energy

938
00:41:40,900 --> 00:41:42,300
from your dance performance back!

939
00:41:42,300 --> 00:41:43,140
Exactly.

940
00:41:43,300 --> 00:41:44,340
- Come again?
- The dance.

941
00:41:44,340 --> 00:41:45,420
- Okay.
- During the dance.

942
00:41:45,420 --> 00:41:46,300
Like we did on stage.

943
00:41:46,580 --> 00:41:47,460
That's a great pose.

944
00:41:48,340 --> 00:41:50,380
Three, two, one.

945
00:41:50,380 --> 00:41:51,260
Cheese!

946
00:41:53,100 --> 00:41:53,940
Nice!

947
00:41:54,740 --> 00:41:56,260
- One more.
- Change your pose.

948
00:41:56,260 --> 00:41:57,160
Let's take another one.

949
00:41:59,860 --> 00:42:02,100
Three, two, one.

950
00:42:02,100 --> 00:42:03,020
Smile!

951
00:42:03,580 --> 00:42:05,460
- Nice!
- I squinted just now.

952
00:42:05,460 --> 00:42:06,460
Let's take another.

953
00:42:06,620 --> 00:42:08,020
Another one, another one!

954
00:42:08,340 --> 00:42:09,220
Let's face that way.

955
00:42:09,540 --> 00:42:11,060
- Okay.
- Hands on your hips.

956
00:42:12,140 --> 00:42:13,300
Head back? Alright.

957
00:42:13,300 --> 00:42:15,300
Three, two, one.

958
00:42:17,060 --> 00:42:17,940
This pose looks great.

959
00:42:17,940 --> 00:42:18,780
Gorgeous!

960
00:42:20,940 --> 00:42:22,580
Another one, another one!

961
00:42:29,780 --> 00:42:32,220
Poured salt into Wu Chunhua's cup?

962
00:42:32,940 --> 00:42:34,140
How dare you do that?

963
00:42:34,260 --> 00:42:35,660
We really did it.

964
00:42:35,940 --> 00:42:37,820
Chen Mo said she'd get revenge for you,

965
00:42:38,140 --> 00:42:40,140
so I joined in and poured a little too.

966
00:42:42,460 --> 00:42:43,980
Did you see her drink it?

967
00:42:44,260 --> 00:42:45,100
No.

968
00:42:45,300 --> 00:42:46,580
It was so close!

969
00:42:47,180 --> 00:42:48,740
When we were halfway through,

970
00:42:48,740 --> 00:42:50,300
she suddenly came back.

971
00:42:50,980 --> 00:42:52,500
Luckily, Lu Yao warned us in time.

972
00:42:52,740 --> 00:42:53,660
I went out

973
00:42:53,980 --> 00:42:55,220
to pretend to interview her.

974
00:42:55,580 --> 00:42:57,540
Then, Lu Yao helped

975
00:42:57,660 --> 00:42:58,580
Chen Mo escape.

976
00:42:58,900 --> 00:43:00,980
But when Chang Wuji

977
00:43:00,980 --> 00:43:02,740
went to the office, he saw it.

978
00:43:03,140 --> 00:43:05,380
He said she immediately spat out the water!

979
00:43:05,700 --> 00:43:06,940
She kept asking

980
00:43:06,940 --> 00:43:08,620
who slipped into the office!

981
00:43:08,620 --> 00:43:10,100
(Jiale Wontons)

982
00:43:10,100 --> 00:43:11,740
How did you guys come up with this idea?

983
00:43:14,300 --> 00:43:15,660
But… Ka Men,

984
00:43:16,900 --> 00:43:17,860
are you feeling better?

985
00:43:21,340 --> 00:43:22,860
You guys were in class all day,

986
00:43:23,090 --> 00:43:24,460
while I had fun all day.

987
00:43:25,500 --> 00:43:26,660
Tomorrow, I'm taking them

988
00:43:26,660 --> 00:43:28,740
to the Jinmao Tower
and the Oriental Pearl Tower.

989
00:43:30,500 --> 00:43:31,900
Aren't you jealous?

990
00:43:34,120 --> 00:43:35,980
Come on!

991
00:43:36,740 --> 00:43:37,660
Don't worry!

992
00:43:38,300 --> 00:43:39,140
Fine.

993
00:43:39,500 --> 00:43:40,340
Well then…

994
00:43:40,820 --> 00:43:41,940
see you tomorrow.

995
00:43:42,420 --> 00:43:43,260
See you tomorrow!

996
00:43:45,900 --> 00:43:46,740
I'm going home now.

997
00:43:48,700 --> 00:43:49,540
Go ahead.

998
00:44:10,940 --> 00:44:14,980
(End of Episode 19)

